\n<br />\n不過我本身都唔中意食海鮮<br />\n身邊啲朋友都中意食海鮮<br />\n唔想佢地全部人就哂我唔嗌<br />\n結果我就望住佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係鮮蝦鮮蟹裏面有野令你敏感，炒飯果啲通常都係脫晒水</blockquote><br />\nOic 長知識了<br />\n淨係蝦蟹先係咁<br />\n蠔呀蜆嗰啲又冇事</blockquote><br />\n係，我朋友都係咁，如果蝦蟹係超級唔新鮮既話佢就食得，所以每次食飯叫蝦蟹都搵佢聞一聞，佢一聞就知新唔新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6754a22b9a65210a86f49bf3e649e5779f4f5cc5","tid":326533,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對海鮮敏感都未算慘<br />\n最慘係你同個對海鮮敏感既人一齊<br />\n而你本身好撚鍾意食海鮮<br />\n但次次食飯都要避忌晒d海鮮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有朋友都係 但次次就佢唔叫海鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下食咩囉<br />\n打冷你整碟海鮮黎即係叫我地食白飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2ec1e624a0f47005bd4f4a165cacd8b2505201","tid":326533,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:17:16.000Z","msg":"除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</span>"},{"pid":"4eb8bc37d69a7540c078e54a29669b377b0d10c6","tid":326533,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</span></blockquote><br />\n你又慘啲。。。平時食雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e21e56af7abf3564f08d579675e3dd64700d31","tid":326533,"uid":742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</span></blockquote><br />\n你又慘啲。。。平時食雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朱古力都唔食得<br />\n真係人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942dbba2ce7aea94b54026308e0f3b49546b80a5","tid":326533,"uid":1786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"其實我真係純粹唔鍾意食海鮮 特別係蝦蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但次次同親fd食飯同佢地講我唔食海鮮都會問我係唔係敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1440e3b892a400cb0291b2ea0b220ed45c1706ff","tid":326533,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我對海鮮敏感<br />\n鮮蝦鮮蟹一食就又紅又痕<br />\n但揚州炒飯啲蝦仁又ok<br />\n<br />\n不過我本身都唔中意食海鮮<br />\n身邊啲朋友都中意食海鮮<br />\n唔想佢地全部人就哂我唔嗌<br />\n結果我就望住佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係鮮蝦鮮蟹裏面有野令你敏感，炒飯果啲通常都係脫晒水</blockquote><br />\nOic 長知識了<br />\n淨係蝦蟹先係咁<br />\n蠔呀蜆嗰啲又冇事</blockquote><br />\n係，我朋友都係咁，如果蝦蟹係超級唔新鮮既話佢就食得，所以每次食飯叫蝦蟹都搵佢聞一聞，佢一聞就知新唔新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇你朋友西利喎<br />\n我就基本用黎炒飯嗰啲先冇咁易敏感<br />\n但食得多都會<br />\n鮮嗰啲就一兩隻就黎料<br />\n<br />\n其實我呢啲對海鮮過敏嘅人都幾慘<br />\n見住人食海鮮，尤其龍蝦<br />\n食到雪雪聲又lam哂手指<br />\n但我地係享受唔到<br />\n少左一樣人生樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205e925c9d2731f1b5dd0895653512f13bb8cbba","tid":326533,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</span></blockquote><br />\n你又慘啲。。。平時食雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朱古力都唔食得<br />\n真係人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雞同豬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家修心養性盡量食得清啲<br />\n之前試過食一塊朱古力之後就仆咗街"},{"pid":"4a9f0587f511a27b67bd65ee09e46192fee3ce9e","tid":326533,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我對海鮮敏感<br />\n鮮蝦鮮蟹一食就又紅又痕<br />\n但揚州炒飯啲蝦仁又ok<br />\n<br />\n不過我本身都唔中意食海鮮<br />\n身邊啲朋友都中意食海鮮<br />\n唔想佢地全部人就哂我唔嗌<br />\n結果我就望住佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係鮮蝦鮮蟹裏面有野令你敏感，炒飯果啲通常都係脫晒水</blockquote><br />\nOic 長知識了<br />\n淨係蝦蟹先係咁<br />\n蠔呀蜆嗰啲又冇事</blockquote><br />\n係，我朋友都係咁，如果蝦蟹係超級唔新鮮既話佢就食得，所以每次食飯叫蝦蟹都搵佢聞一聞，佢一聞就知新唔新鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇你朋友西利喎<br />\n我就基本用黎炒飯嗰啲先冇咁易敏感<br />\n但食得多都會<br />\n鮮嗰啲就一兩隻就黎料<br />\n<br />\n其實我呢啲對海鮮過敏嘅人都幾慘<br />\n見住人食海鮮，尤其龍蝦<br />\n食到雪雪聲又lam哂手指<br />\n但我地係享受唔到<br />\n少左一樣人生樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都有其它可以食既，貝殼類仲有其它，我問過朋友佢話唔恨食，可能本身都無食過唔知係咩味掛"},{"pid":"c79c52f91c6b75fb709c718b6070da25bb749438","tid":326533,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</span></blockquote><br />\n你又慘啲。。。平時食雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朱古力都唔食得<br />\n真係人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗係奶類敏感<br />\n仲撚慘<br />\n好多野都唔食得"},{"pid":"ed3330aba9f1b4549214067a0395d8af7d17c0ed","tid":326533,"uid":109159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除咗魚之外乜海鮮都唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">牛同朱古力都唔得呀屌</